Mana-Table Component Spec: Deck & Arc-Hand Overlay
1. The Arc-Hand (Overlay Layer)
The Hand lives on a fixed HUD layer, independent of the infinite canvas zoom/pan. It is designed to feel physical and organic.

A. Visual Styling & Geometry

Container-less Design: No visible box; cards float directly at the bottom of the viewport.

The "Peek" State: By default, cards are tucked off-screen, with only the top 20% visible.

Hover Reveal: Hovering near the bottom edge triggers a vertical slide-up (translateY) to reveal the full cards.

The Fan (Rotational Arc): * Cards are distributed along a subtle arc.

The leftmost card is rotated -5°.

The rightmost card is rotated 5°.

